This directory contains build resources specific to the Mac OS X
platform.  There are related Mac OS X build scripts of interest also
located in the top-level sh directory (make_pkg.sh & make_dmg.sh) as
well as the top-level Makefile.am build targets: make pkg & make dmg


README
	this file

Resources/
	contains the files for an Installer .pkg including the
	ReadMe, Welcome, License, and any installation support
	scripts.

background.png
	the background image for the .dmg installation images.

openUp.c
	a .dmg helper program used by sh/make_dmg.sh to force the
	disk mounting image to automatically open up a window when it
	is mounted.
